{"tid":83413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得岩岩做朋友到成為情人....","createTime":"2017-01-16T17:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T12:05:49.000Z","uid":3333,"like":54,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1267c2a020ff5d4edd31ab615d104ec68744ffdc","tid":83413,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"正評：3個月內唔一齊就會發展成朋友<br />\n負評：慢慢識落了解左先，可能做一年以上普通朋友再一齊"},{"pid":"9f876132a908a61d769c2127005bf17e9c7c5b17","tid":83413,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55fd99f019c3bc63df25aedeecf0b03ec946766","tid":83413,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"做得太耐朋友係無可能變情人<br />\n之前同個男仔好夾 傾左3個月 好多共同話題<br />\n之後一齊左一個禮拜 分左手<br />\n個模式唔同左 相處唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做朋友係非常好 一變情人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後朋友都做唔成"},{"pid":"0fbff5158c71172127e2bc5920e0f117d8449432","tid":83413,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己係去到咁上下地步大家都無前進一步<br />\n或者卡住左喺某個位嘅話<br />\n最後就會好自然淡左/變成朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過有幾個曾經相處幾曖昧<br />\n都肯定佢對我有好感嘅男仔<br />\n因為拖得太耐無進展，就會覺得之前係錯覺。本來幾sweet嘅曖昧都變成左「習慣」，無左一開始個種心動嘅感覺。"},{"pid":"f6dc42db3e1971364b8b23d792324c9c2683d890","tid":83413,"uid":10354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己係去到咁上下地步大家都無前進一步<br />\n或者卡住左喺某個位嘅話<br />\n最後就會好自然淡左/變成朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過有幾個曾經相處幾曖昧<br />\n都肯定佢對我有好感嘅男仔<br />\n因為拖得太耐無進展，就會覺得之前係錯覺。本來幾sweet嘅曖昧都變成左「習慣」，無左一開始個種心動嘅感覺。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，拖太耐搞到本身有feel都變無feel，而且仲會諗返轉頭點解初初會對佢有好感，已經唔記得自己點解會鍾意佢"},{"pid":"e7ce95ee6dc3efff00ea0249dae4a6dacbe8f052","tid":83413,"uid":21622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"做左年幾fd 大家都第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41752fd455c338765fd03f565b3c0ca579a028c","tid":83413,"uid":23431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"3個月算唔算耐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6588b14aff68b4f20bf906c9f3964fdab2f324d","tid":83413,"uid":76094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"正評 覺得傾左成年了解哂只可以be fd"},{"pid":"11a15d745ba0819f970551e00e7868aa24daffe4","tid":83413,"uid":67082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"好睇人 根本個個唔同"},{"pid":"896f31537f8663b26838205b206d83b7e7438d5e","tid":83413,"uid":77279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得太耐朋友係無可能變情人<br />\n之前同個男仔好夾 傾左3個月 好多共同話題<br />\n之後一齊左一個禮拜 分左手<br />\n個模式唔同左 相處唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做朋友係非常好 一變情人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後朋友都做唔成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係興趣班到識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ceec11fb73e5de991c4ad86c6b1161f49a4f6b4e","tid":83413,"uid":20842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">現實</span>：3個月內唔一齊就會發展成朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">理想</span>：慢慢識落了解左先，可能做一年以上普通朋友再一齊"},{"pid":"f5623095141560eb86430d54f5b1ca47a240b698","tid":83413,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">現實</span>：3個月內唔一齊就會發展成朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">理想</span>：慢慢識落了解左先，可能做一年以上普通朋友再一齊</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680cb25c335c7f2806130421736275b8d8a1f535","tid":83413,"uid":68487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得太耐朋友係無可能變情人<br />\n之前同個男仔好夾 傾左3個月 好多共同話題<br />\n之後一齊左一個禮拜 分左手<br />\n個模式唔同左 相處唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做朋友係非常好 一變情人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後朋友都做唔成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ni know that feel......<br />\n同個女仔fd識咗好多年<br />\n早排大家多咗機會見面<br />\n一齊咗唔夠一個月就分開咗<br />\n但其實相處得開心<br />\n只係佢話唔習慣朋友變情人<br />\n暫時仲係朋友<br />\n但唔會點whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bb308d23c5b01fefb7348708c9cb948dd0ebfc","tid":83413,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"理想既緊係由好fd變男女朋友<br />\n但其實做朋友做耐左真係會無左feel<br />\n自己試過兩次<br />\n有一次係鍾意左識左唔算好耐既男仔<br />\n之後發現佢有女朋友  就超唔開心<br />\n但一年之後佢散左<br />\n果陣我已經對佢完全無晒感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一個男仔都係一樣  唯一唔同只係佢未散 仲拍緊<br />\n而家同呢個男仔好fd<br />\n發現自己對佢都已經無晒感覺<br />\n只係朋友上既喜歡  完全講唔上係愛情<br />\n所以最好都係幾個月之內發展成為情侶啦"},{"pid":"9881cbe0cf33f9625cd4fa1c2738aaa54271ac22","tid":83413,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"[quote]<span style=\"color: red;\">現實</span>：3個月內唔一齊就會發展成朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">理想</span>：慢慢識落了解左先，可能做一年以上普通朋友再一齊[/quote］<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我都friend zone 咗你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMe:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0342ab374368234943fe190da8747cd82db59b4","tid":83413,"uid":20842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"諗唔通點解會咁<br />\n無左感覺都仲可以係一個理由 <br />\n但如果仲有feel呢？<br />\n點解好似過左個期限就番唔到轉頭？<br />\n點解朋友做唔到情侶？"},{"pid":"f43df1d17b62a90a457d124e864d5e0281e97799","tid":83413,"uid":19134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55f00b13282acde7efc7e5056700d972625adc0","tid":83413,"uid":18944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">現實</span>：3個月內唔一齊就會發展成朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">理想</span>：慢慢識落了解左先，可能做一年以上普通朋友再一齊</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到"},{"pid":"058688bf90166f5f67f2ef29d70118649acbd54a","tid":83413,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"緣份"},{"pid":"2e1692562aacb358d89f5e58a8e64c807a1316f0","tid":83413,"uid":37080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"識左六年入埋大學先一齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c531e5257ddb1235e073dbd0ed99c7b4cf1d837","tid":83413,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"變咗朋友分咗就連朋友都無埋"},{"pid":"7e3bee08d889a1c346f55677eee9c3590c481911","tid":83413,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"見過六，七次面 食過二